  "response_text": "Inside a brightly lit refrigerator, food and drinks are arranged like a small stage. A blue Ensure Original nutrition shake bottle and a white Ensure Max Protein carton stand upright in the center, both animated with small white arms. Around them are an orange juice carton, condiments, broccoli, tomatoes, an onion, jars, and other refrigerator items. The Ensure Max Protein carton is white with purple and brown accents and a chocolate splash at the bottom of the label; it faces forward as the featured product, while the blue Ensure bottle stands nearby.\n\nThe white Ensure Max Protein carton moves into prominence among the other refrigerator items. A large on-screen graphic appears to its right reading “MORE ENERGY in just 2 WEEKS,” with the number 2 inside a purple circle and radiating lines around it. A sliced orange sits in the foreground, and an anthropomorphic tomato-like character with eyes is partly visible to the right. A thin line of small disclaimer text runs along the bottom of the image. The Max Protein carton raises one arm with a confident, presenting gesture, standing in front of milk jugs, broccoli, and condiments.\n\nThe scene shifts to another part of the refrigerator. A yellow pear with tiny eyes and white arms stands beside the tall orange juice carton. The blue Ensure Original bottle is partly visible on the left. The pear reaches toward the orange juice carton as if trying to handle it. The Ensure Max Protein carton appears from the right side of the orange juice carton and begins to take hold of it, placing its white arms against the carton. The orange juice carton is large and yellow-orange, with a splash design and the words “orange juice” near the top. As the Max Protein carton pushes or carries it aside, the pear watches. The orange juice carton slides across the refrigerator shelf, revealing celery stalks, a carrot, and a smiling banana behind it. The pear relaxes and smiles while the Max Protein carton continues moving the juice carton, leaning into the effort with its arms stretched out.\n\nThe imagery then becomes a close-up of a creamy chocolate-colored drink pouring into a pool of the same liquid. The stream plunges into the surface, creating a rounded splash, ripples, and droplets. The liquid looks thick and glossy, with warm brown highlights. As the pouring continues, a blue rectangular graphic appears on the right reading “30g PROTEIN” in white and dark lettering. The chocolate liquid swirls and splashes around the pouring stream. A second blue graphic appears below it reading “1g SUGAR,” emphasizing the nutrition numbers while the drink continues to ripple and bubble.\n\nThe commercial ends on a clean product display against a light blue background. Three Ensure Max Protein cartons stand side by side: milk chocolate, French vanilla, and café mocha. Small flavor-related items sit in front of them, including chocolate pieces, a vanilla flower, and coffee beans or mocha pieces. To the right, the Ensure logo appears with the words “STRENGTH & ENERGY.” Beneath it is a colorful circular graphic labeled for immune system support, with nutrient names around the ring, including protein, vitamins, zinc, and vitamin D. A small footnote at the bottom mentions vitamins C and E as part of a healthy diet, along with Abbott copyright text.",
